{"tid":1074363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人 一個另一半幫你出頭既經歷","createTime":"2019-03-23T10:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T16:17:27.000Z","uid":201495,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b9170896d8548549b50af50afc5a53bbbdd777e","tid":1074363,"uid":201495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"我先，中五個時有個ABC女朋友<br />\n個時玩打鼓機，我跟機<br />\n之後有個MK無視我直接入錢坐低<br />\n我女朋友問唔係應該輪到我咩<br />\n我話係呀算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後女朋友半秒0至300暴走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用英文喪屌條MK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌撚到個MK選完歌都唔敢打起身俾棍我<br />\n<br />\n暴後首歌我打唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n20秒極速收皮俾返$5個MK就走左<br />\n<br />\n後尾問條女佢請左咩<br />\n佢話塞個玻璃樽入個MK屎眼再踢爆佢之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baddc6d506dbec58955e85bcd0e4191073dd0c60","tid":1074363,"uid":201495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e886ed5b6de10bef4128a55ef069f8e562e526ca","tid":1074363,"uid":205775,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"去游水見到對mk情侶 <br />\n條女係咁啤住我 仲發自己條仔脾氣話望我<br />\n之後兩個走左出去 <br />\n我估條仔要氹番條女 <br />\n<br />\n一陣之後 佢地番黎 <br />\n條女繼續啤我<br />\n之後我同男友講 <br />\n佢好大聲咁話 ：人地咁撚7緊係鍾意啤你 無料先會啤人<br />\n<br />\n之後條仔衝過黎打我條仔 又撻朵跟邊到邊到<br />\n之後好快趣閃人 <br />\n之後我地同救生員講報警 成班救生員截住佢 7撚到<br />\n之後成班警察屌9佢 要佢地同我地道歉 <br />\n<br />\n聽番先知 條仔有案底 媽 我好撚驚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}